{{#is_alert}}

## What's happening?
Content repository utilization on NiFi host {{host.name}} has exceeded 85% over the last 15 minutes.

When the content repository fills completely, NiFi stops accepting new data. Consider:
- Clearing completed FlowFiles that are no longer needed
- Adding additional content repository directories in `nifi.properties`
- Investigating stuck flows that may be accumulating data

{{/is_alert}}

{{#is_warning}}
Content repository utilization on NiFi host {{host.name}} has exceeded 75%.
{{/is_warning}}

{{#is_recovery}}
Content repository utilization on {{host.name}} has returned to normal.
{{/is_recovery}}
